title: Affordable Corner Garden Lvl 1-br nr U, Downtown, River Trails;parking
posting_body: ['Corner GARDEN-LEVEL one-bedroom apartment in well-maintained 12-unit building with rent that includes off-street parking.', 'Corner windows offer daylight; other features include full-size appliances, ceiling fan, AIR-CONDITIONER, window blinds, and ample closets; on-site laundry, and one off-street parking space.', '(Pictures resemble available apartment.)', 'EXCELLENT LOCATION:  One block to convenience store/deli and bus stop.', 'Three blocks to Stone Arch Bridge and to walking/biking trails along Mississippi.', 'Just one-mile walk, bus or bike to U of M, Dinkytown and downtown Minneapolis.', 'Short walk to Marcy Holmes Park, Lunds Grocery Store, and St. Anthony Falls shops and restaurants, including R Taco, Brasa, and Herbivorous Butcher.', 'TERMS:', 'Two-person maximum and additional monthly rent for second person.', 'Rent includes one OFF-STREET PARKING space.', 'Rent also includes heat, water, sewer, and household trash.', 'Resident pays monthly electricity.', "Damage deposit equal to one month's rent due at lease signing.", "First month's rent due on lease start date.", ' Application fee: $30 per adult.', 'One cat o.k. with payment of pet rent $20 per month.', 'Sorry, no dogs.', 'When you reply by email, please tell us: 1.', 'how many adults and children?', '2. preferred move-in date?', '3. does anyone smoke?', '4.', 'any animals or pets?', '5.', 'your telephone number and email address.', 'Thank you']
